    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! Are you looking for a reliable ride that\u2019s ready for its next big adventure? I\u2019m parting with my car, and it has been such a joy to drive! It\u2019s in solid shape and has been well-cared for, meaning it\u2019s got plenty of life left in it. It runs beautifully and is perfect for daily commutes or weekend getaways. Come take it for a spin\u2014you\u2019re going to love how it feels on the road!",
      "price": 32500.0,
