      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 8
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "Available for the discerning driver is this E92 M3, featuring the high-revving S65 4.0L naturally aspirated V8 and a tactile 6-speed manual transmission. This specimen maintains its mechanical integrity with a linear power band and an 8,400 RPM redline. The chassis retains its composure through M-specific aluminum suspension geometry and an active M Variable Differential Lock. Key preventative maintenance has been addressed, including rod bearing replacement with upgraded shells and new throttle actuators to ensure the independent throttle bodies operate flawlessly. While showing minor signs of use consistent with a well-driven enthusiast vehicle, the Electronic Damper Control (EDC) and hydraulic steering rack provide a communicative and precise driving experience. This is a mechanically stout example of the final naturally aspirated M3.",
